title: New: Lana Del Rey – National Anthem
content:
With just under a month until the release of her debut LP Born To Die, another track set to feature on the record has found it’s way onto the internet.

It’s an upbeat, R’n’B styled number, quite GaGa-esque in nature if I’m honest, but in typical Lana fashion, it just works. Whether these staggered leaks are a ploy to keep the blogosphere buzzing or someone out there has a personal vendetta to settle, who knows, either way, it’s certainly serving to build anticipation for her upcoming record. Check out National Anthem below.
